# Runtime dependencies for the ClusterFuzzLite fuzz build (.clusterfuzzlite).
# The local camt053 package is added to PyInstaller's --paths instead of being
# pip-installed, so only its third-party runtime deps are pinned here. These are
# everything the fuzzed entry points (camt053.services and the parse/profile/
# schema/validation modules it imports) need to import successfully.
